{
  "texts": [
    "It is necessary to verify how the service descriptions, needs, and upcycling cases presented in this study contribute to the efficiency of service development, and then refine the model based on the results.",
    "ConclusionThis study aimed to explore a method for efficiently developing services that meet user needs, starting from the user's active speech.",
    "The focus was on constructing a system that discovers the outline of the services users desire and the technologies that aid in their development.",
    "By improving upon prior research, we achieved the identification of service overviews through the extraction of user needs for unknown services and the discovery of useful technologies via keyword searches based on upcycle case needs.",
    "Through experiments and detailed analysis, we found that the proposed method demonstrates excellent capability in presenting development information when ideal speech is provided."
  ]
}